                href="https://www.flaticon.com/"
                rel="nofollow"
                target="_blank">Flaticon.com</a
              > (soumises à leur licence).
              <ul class="legal">
                <li>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.flaticon.com/fr/icone-gratuite/nager_7115059?related_id=7115059"
